timing_suppre...int_mismatches(25.10)    timing_suppre...int_mismatches(25.10)

Name
       timing_suppress_ilm_constraint_mismatches

Syntax
       timing_suppress_ilm_constraint_mismatches

       {true | false}

       Default: false

       When  set  to  true, the software suppresses all error and warning mes-
       sages related to objects not found when loading  SDC  constraint  files
       for the ILM flow.

       In  the  current ILM flow, SDC constraints originally specified against
       the complete flat netlist for the design do not get filtered when being
       applied against the ILM view of the design. Constraints that  reference
       parts  of  the design that were pruned cause warnings and errors during
       constraint loading.

       To set this global variable, use the set_global command.

